{"tid":2421331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2012 - 2014 係唔係香港最有願景既兩年？","createTime":"2021-02-24T12:24:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T20:41:19.000Z","uid":154486,"like":16,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a126acaa95ba8d63025d02bb49fa2abfb6f7707f","tid":2421331,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T12:24:05.000Z","msg":"近牌睇番狂舞派1<br />\n當時係覺得好貼地<br />\n發覺而家睇番已經好天真<br />\n<br />\n2012既香港人我諗大約都係咁<br />\n2013年梁振英上台，HKTV咁多當時睇落去劃時代既劇集，比好多人見到原來唔駛睇TVB，原來D劇集可以做到咁樣<br />\n2014年雨傘，你話金鐘左膠都好，但係佢地真係做到一個烏托邦<br />\n<br />\n天真有時都唔係壞事，有過曾經既希望好過乜都冇"},{"pid":"a3350ae3fe88704bb63d595f1f12cb71827726ad","tid":2421331,"uid":136431,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T12:26:07.000Z","msg":"2012 國教係會擱置 有個錯覺 <br />\n覺得單純嘅集會示威係有用"},{"pid":"14a57b89fdb0d45757f1cf01ea72f983b26ab6fb","tid":2421331,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a3350ae3fe88704bb63d595f1f12cb71827726ad","tid":2421331,"uid":136431,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T12:26:07.000Z","msg":"2012 國教係會擱置 有個錯覺 <br />\n覺得單純嘅集會示威係有用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T12:27:34.000Z","msg":"我覺得個錯覺雖然係錯覺，但係亦都證明左果個就係香港最理想既未來"},{"pid":"d4bd98701993ac6e0f6f4b8c52d02a6a9d130c0e","tid":2421331,"uid":70487,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T12:29:28.000Z","msg":"就嚟十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"399645477e175bdebda496cb1605ec69cd7113bd","tid":2421331,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T12:30:55.000Z","msg":"而家就算係要走既<br />\n相信好多人都記得當時果種好有希望既感覺<br />\n<br />\n呢樣真正既初心<br />\n希望大家要keep住"},{"pid":"3e5a459a630bd214831987b0401d0558f44dabe0","tid":2421331,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4bd98701993ac6e0f6f4b8c52d02a6a9d130c0e","tid":2421331,"uid":70487,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T12:29:28.000Z","msg":"就嚟十年<img src=\"/assets/f